{"tid":532770,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"魅族發布全新LIVE耳機！4動鐵$1299！","createTime":"2018-01-18T07:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T12:03:49.000Z","uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c93bb45156a990f8eda36cd37ba9e450fa66802d","tid":532770,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/151909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F151909_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1f6578c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/151918_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F151918_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=564b6c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n魅族發布全新LIVE耳機！4動鐵$1299！<br />\n2018-01-17 2074<br />\n<br />\n手機新品發布會魅族總會帶來一些有意思的配件，這次伴隨魅藍S6而來的，是兩款新耳機。首先是魅族LIVE耳機，最大特點是採用了樓氏四動鐵定制單元，確保還原每個頻段的真實聲音，並有低頻平衡電樞、中高頻平衡電樞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n它擁有雙通管道技術，MMCX通用接口，配套三種管嘴套件，可根據聽歌喜好選擇均衡、明亮、飽滿三種不同頻率的聲音，售價1299元，19日10點開賣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其次是魅族Flowbass耳機，面向低頻發燒友，全新的Bass+系統，三單元從結構到發聲全面調整，專為低頻而作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n它還採用聲學濾網增密設計，提升低頻透氣效率，搭配石墨烯複合振膜，低音更澎湃，現場感更強，內部為E-Audio EK-61810動鐵和復合振膜動圈，售價599元。"},{"pid":"9391f2291e61c4eeb368225b92fb63dceafed2fd","tid":532770,"uid":653,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62eafca35aef2225c8793748df65cbd107d7e604","tid":532770,"uid":53776,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"846<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif